wsrc%5Etfw\">@KnownOrigin_io<\/a> next week! For more details, click here: <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/GdPtgNEOZb\">https:\/\/t.co\/GdPtgNEOZb<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Portrait of LIFE\u2019s first hired staff and female photographer, Margaret Bourke-White, 1943.<\/p>\n<p>(\ud83d\udcf7 Alfred Eisenstaedt \/ LIFE Picture Collection ) <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/6sD3HtQQGB\">pic.twitter.com\/6sD3HtQQGB<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u2014 LIFE (@LIFE) <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/LIFE\/status\/1510995812070961161?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 4, 2022<\/a><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>KnownOrigin\u2019s launch will initially see a set of ultra-rare NFTs auctioned to the highest bidder. Then followed by a set of limited editions with a fixed price for the wider audience. Following the sale, <strong>the team will neutralize all minting and sales emissions<\/strong> via a carbon offset program, while a portion of proceeds will benefit a range of worthy causes chosen by the good folk over at LIFE. The first of which will see disadvantaged girls learn to read via the <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/MalalaFund\">Malala Fund<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Learn more &gt;&gt; <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.life.com\/history\/life-launches-collection-of-nfts-from-iconic-photographs\/\">Here<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><b>Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/ecadf05eb1bf\/1\">Join the Weekly Newsletter<br \/><\/a><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/qSQwMaM\">Join our Discord<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/nftplazas\">Follow us on Twitter<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/nf